data.meta_description: Wether you're a guest, or committed member, you're family to us! You can learn more about NewSong, Watch livestreams, Give/Donate, See our weekly schedule and Contact us here!
data.text:
Click the on the button below to either register your kiddos or volunteer to serve!

A Space Explorer has searched all over the universe for other life. He has come to continue his search for other life and the light of the world. Memory Verse: "When Jesus spoke again to the people, he said, I am the light of the world. Whoever follows me will never walk in darkness, but will have the light of life."
